{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"53196bed6a","title":"秋声辞","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a12db1aba4","index":0,"year":1963,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"53196bed6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c5892196e2","name":"林昭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c0a14eddc","type":"title","text":"秋声辞","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"46828b1e78","type":"authors","text":"北京大学林昭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"f178eb789a","type":"subtitle","text":"秋声辞  并序","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"4c6d0b4f47","type":"paragraph","text":"在狱三秋，佗傺长恨；秋心秋睹，郁作秋声。即用鉴湖女侠断句为韵，并作辘轳体以敷陈其意，有愿补石，不避续貂，；回还往复，声气尚应；后其再来人欤，抑前贤绿烈之荫也！哀时明志，未辨今昔，成仁取义，誓继会武！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"e6369c086f","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九六三年十月林昭自志","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"9efdde2d68","type":"paragraph","text":"秋风秋雨愁杀人，凭对遥天吊甘荆撩：狐鼠纵横山岳老，脂青滴沥稻粱贫，为悲寂寞求同气，敢避艰难惜一身？夜夜肠回寒蛰泣，丹心未忍逐青怜！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"fd99bb451c","type":"paragraph","text":"劫里芳华不成春，秋风秋雨愁煞人！青衫泪悒朱颜悴，碧血花催白发新，决死精卫战浩荡，伤心子规哭沉沦！齐家报国犹虚说，愧负望做父老亲！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"d0eab8fee7","type":"paragraph","text":"哀江南赋墨浩尘，，抱恨楚囚志未伸，霾貉霾霜瘦生气，秋风秋雨愁煞人，宁随兆遮望朔口，岂戴独夫谲佞臣？唱彻招魂金铁寂，肝肠百沸温罗巾！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"b021eaaa5a","type":"paragraph","text":"忧乐苍生夙愿真，壮怀激烈照天陈；吞帽谁复思侯汉？蹈海我终不帝秦！赤水赤原病休国，秋风秋雨愁煞人！此身定化干城剑，贯日横空泣鬼神！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"a6237b20f3","type":"paragraph","text":"浩歌慷慨夺江津，最是知音第五伦，翰墨请缨彰素去，榛卷补石证前因，凌霜劲节千钧义，捍刃英谋一念仁！莫笑猖狂乔作态，秋风秋雨愁煞人！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"},{"id":"65548fe37c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《林昭文抄》，甘粹先生2000年7月11日抄本。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a"}],"page":{"id":"89034d34d2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"53196bed6a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}